<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>About WanderWise</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="./img/chatbot.png" />
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #1f242d;
      color: #ecf0f1;
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #0ef;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: #1f242d;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .about-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 72px);
    }

    .left-content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 4rem;
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      animation: slideIn 1s ease forwards;
    }

    .right-image {
      flex: 1;
      background: #0ef;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .right-image img {
      width: 350px;
      height: 350px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 8px solid white;
      object-fit: cover;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      animation: popIn 1s ease;
    }

    .right-image .caption {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #1f242d;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    h1, h3 {
      color: #0ef;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }

    @keyframes popIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: scale(0.8);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scale(1);
      }
    }

    @keyframes slideIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-wrapper {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .left-content, .right-image {
        flex: none;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .right-image img {
        width: 250px;
        height: 250px;
      }

      .right-image .caption {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">
      <a href="/">WanderWise AI</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-wrapper">
    <div class="left-content">
      <h1>About WanderWise</h1>
      <p><strong>WanderWise</strong> is a solo project built by <strong>Anup Pandey</strong> to intelligently assist travelers in planning adventures with real-time, personalized suggestions using AI.</p>

      <p>This chatbot is powered by <strong>Gemini 1.5 Flash API</strong>, enabling fast and accurate travel recommendations based on natural language input. Whether you're into hiking, diving, or road-tripping, WanderWise delivers smart, curated suggestions tailored to your interests.</p>

      <h3>Core Features:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Tailored adventure trip planning</li>
        <li>AI-based destination and activity ideas</li>
        <li>Fast, friendly interaction with Gemini 1.5 Flash</li>
        <li>Solo-built backend and frontend integration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="right-image">
      <img src="/img/anup.jpg" alt="Anup Pandey" />
      <div class="caption">
        <div>Crafted with <span style="color: red;">‚ù§</span> by <strong>Anup Pandey</strong></div>
        <div style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: #444;">Powered by Gemini 1.5 Flash API</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>